                td Monday 20 July 2020

          p Bookings will be made available three weeks before the term starts and will close on the last day of term. The exception to this will be during summer holidays ready for Term 1.
          p This means that Term 1 bookings will be made available on 12th August and will close on Friday 30th August.
          p All registered users will receive an email reminding them of the day that bookings open and again two days before the bookings shut.
          p To complete a booking you will need credit on your Libacura account. Funds can be added to your account through the Libacura website using GoCardless, BACS or Childcare Vouchers.
          p If you are eligible for childcare vouchers or tax-free childcare, please make sure that you order your vouchers in advance so that your account has credit before the termly deadline for bookings.
          
          h4 Making ad-hoc bookings
          p If during the term you realise that you need or have forgotten a date, please send an email at least three days in advance and we will see if there is space for your child to attend.
          
          h3 Holiday Club bookings 
          p Libacura enables you to book your preferred sessions for Holiday Club. If the session you want is full, you will be put on a waiting list and we will notify you when a space becomes available. Book early to avoid disappointment and to take advantage of our Early Bird discount of 10% off, if booked two weeks before the holiday starts.
          p
            strong All bookings for Holiday Club must be paid for at the time of booking. Please use one of the payment methods below.
          p For further enquiries, please email us at #[a(href='mailto:coopsparks@gmail.com') coopsparks@gmail.com].

        section
          h2#howtopay How to pay
          p Once you have made your booking with us you can pay using any of the following methods:
          ul
            li
              h4 Bank transfer
              p For details, please #[a(href='mailto:coopsparks@gmail.com') email us] or call us on #[a(href='tel:01179244439') 0117 924 4439].
            li
              h4 Childcare vouchers
              p Sparks accepts all recognised childcare vouchers:
